anks have a BP that give them regen, and one that gives them regrowth.  Wheres the casters clarity (well at least they have flowing thought, but WAY harder to get than a fungi tunic)and c2 robes.  VI needs to put items into the game that give 10% cast time increase, and other ones that increase spell effects like 10% damage increase on spells, or 10% mana cost reduction.  Velious quest armor also needs changing for casters.  Most of the pieces arent much better then Apothic, some isnt even as good as apothic.  The tank armor is much better then old planes armor because all of it has a good AC increase.  Caster armor doesnt even have that, with the exception of Kael Quests, but the increase isnt that much and, the stats are crap. <p><table border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1">
