<i>"Summon someone who gives a damn"</i></td></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ureaorn1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reaorn1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#333333>(5/15/01 1:38:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=103.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Caster loot **** SUCKS!!! &gt;:{</span><hr size=1> The issue with this game is quite simple really:<br>
<br>
